             Styles.mobileBlock,
             CssHelper.flexBox(~justify=`center, ~direction=`column, ()),
           ])}>
           <Icon name="fal fa-exclamation-circle" size=32 color=Colors.bandBlue />
           <Text value="Schema not found" color=Colors.gray7 />
         </div>
       </div>,
     );
